{"tid":603738,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 港匯快到危險位 金管局突然有人離職","createTime":"2018-03-24T04:27:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-24T08:46:53.000Z","uid":54373,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0e6cc6deeade8e2ce0a631895976805b5f43e00e","tid":603738,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T04:27:51.000Z","msg":"劉中健接替劉發任金管局助理總裁 <br />\n<br />\n金管局宣布，財政司司長根據外滙基金諮詢委員會轄下管治委員會建議，批准委任劉中健為助理總裁(貨幣管理)，於6月27日生效。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劉中健將負責金管局宏觀金融監察和市場運作以維持金融和貨幣穩定的工作，以及對儲值支付工具和零售支付系統的監管。他將<span style=\"color: red;\">接替基於個人理由辭職的鄭發</span>。<br />\n<br />\n金管局總裁陳德霖表示，對鄭發離任感到非常可惜，並稱他在多個領域的工作貢獻良多。"},{"pid":"373e2e39b70e769b6e9157ae1c9ebfbe8a91fe72","tid":603738,"uid":82640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T04:29:24.000Z","msg":"咁大敵當前唔想OT唔代表唔夠打嘅<br />\n機械式操作<br />\n贏就贏輸就輸"},{"pid":"7df4a780a8262d7b6b77117a9213f79435220ef7","tid":603738,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T04:48:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa47be0a25ee92a067e5c0c04018ffc7c6232713","tid":603738,"uid":79887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T04:50:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 走先"},{"pid":"c57b0a82a515e822dc2afd873850738206776d65","tid":603738,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T04:53:13.000Z","msg":"劉中健將負責金管局宏觀金融監察和市場運作以維持金融和貨幣穩定的工作，以及<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對儲值支付工具和零售支付系統的監管。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n之前金管局搞咩咩pay係同支國競爭<br />\n依家換自己人上去控制番？"},{"pid":"078c39f58a7f313bed6d03f24ca95e5d78e9fbd1","tid":603738,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T05:26:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">識睇一定睇：<br 